mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Date Book", "On the Record and Record Report", "Feature Fashion", "As I See It", "Some Memorable Moments in Square Dancing", "16th National Convention", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "The Caller's Responsibility", "Ladies on the Square", "The 'Rice Paddy Promenaders' of Okinawa", "Interview: The Allens Look at Square Dancing", "Style Series: Let's Talk Awkward vs. Comfort", "Round the World of Square Dancing", "SIO Workshop", "Caller of the Month: 'Red' Bates", "Paging the Round Dancers: Phil and Norma Roberts", and "Experimental Lab: Experimenting With the Traditional".
